## Stack

- **Framework:** Next.js 15 (App Router)
- **Auth:** Clerk
- **DB:** Supabase Postgres + Prisma
- **Payments:** Stripe
- **Email:** Resend
- **Cache + ratelimit:** Upstash Redis
- **Vector search:** Pinecone
- **Analytics:** PostHog
- **Errors:** Sentry
- **i18n:** next-intl
- **UI:** Tailwind v4 + shadcn/ui
- **Monorepo:** Turborepo + pnpm

## Getting started

```bash
pnpm install
cp .env.example .env.local              # then paste real keys
pnpm db:push                            # apply Prisma schema
pnpm dev                                # http://localhost:3000
```

See [`docs/setup.md`](./docs/setup.md) for the per-service signup walkthrough and [`docs/checklist.md`](./docs/checklist.md) for the launch checklist.

## Layout

```
apps/web                # Next.js app
